---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Primorum — Free AI Operations Audit"
  description="Get a free audit of your business operations. We identify the AI software you could integrate to increase revenue and reduce costs — a no-obligation consultation."
>
  <p class="eyebrow">Primorum</p>

  <h1 class="hero">
    A free audit of every place AI could be working for your business right now.
  </h1>

  <p class="lede">
    Most businesses are sitting on operational processes that AI could handle today
    &mdash; and they don't know it. Primorum audits your workflows end-to-end and
    delivers a concrete report: what to integrate, what it would cost, and what
    it would return. No pitch. No commitment. Just the facts.
  </p>

  <p class="cta-block">
    <a class="cta" href="mailto:audit@primorum.ai?subject=Free%20AI%20Operations%20Audit">Request your free audit &rarr;</a>
    <span class="cta-note">You'll hear back within one business day.</span>
  </p>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>What we audit</h2>

  <p class="lede">
    We look at the operational layer of your business &mdash; the repetitive work
    that happens between systems, between people, and between departments.
  </p>

  <ul class="bets">
    <li>
      <p class="label">Customer operations</p>
      <p class="claim">
        Onboarding, support triage, follow-up sequences, churn detection.
        AI can handle the first two tiers of customer interaction today.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="label">Revenue workflows</p>
      <p class="claim">
        Lead qualification, proposal generation, pipeline management, renewal
        timing. AI can compress sales cycles without adding headcount.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="label">Back-office processes</p>
      <p class="claim">
        Invoice processing, expense categorization, compliance checks, report
        generation. AI eliminates the manual stitching between tools.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="label">Data &amp; reporting</p>
      <p class="claim">
        Data extraction from documents, cross-system reconciliation, dashboard
        population, anomaly detection. AI turns scattered data into decisions.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="label">Communications</p>
      <p class="claim">
        Email drafting, meeting summaries, stakeholder updates, internal
        knowledge retrieval. AI keeps information moving without bottlenecks.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="label">Hiring &amp; people ops</p>
      <p class="claim">
        Candidate screening, onboarding document generation, policy Q&A,
        training material adaptation. AI scales the people function.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>What you get</h2>

  <ul class="rules">
    <li>
      <p class="num">01</p>
      <p class="rule">An inventory of AI-ready processes.</p>
      <p>
        A prioritized list of your operational workflows ranked by AI
        suitability, with the ones that would move revenue first.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="num">02</p>
      <p class="rule">Specific software recommendations.</p>
      <p>
        For each workflow, we name the tools &mdash; off-the-shelf, custom, or
        API-integrated &mdash; that could handle it. No vague suggestions.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="num">03</p>
      <p class="rule">Estimated cost and return.</p>
      <p>
        Implementation cost ranges and projected ROI per recommendation, so you
        know which ones pencil out before you spend anything.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="num">04</p>
      <p class="rule">An implementation roadmap.</p>
      <p>
        A phased plan: what to do first, what depends on what, and how long
        each phase takes. Start with the highest-return, lowest-risk move.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>How it works</h2>

  <ol class="steps">
    <li>
      <p class="step-num">1</p>
      <div>
        <p class="step-title">You reach out.</p>
        <p>
          Send a note describing your business and what you'd like us to look
          at. A sentence or two is enough.
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="step-num">2</p>
      <div>
        <p class="step-title">We talk (30 minutes).</p>
        <p>
          A brief call to understand your operations, your tools, and where
          you feel the friction. No prep needed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="step-num">3</p>
      <div>
        <p class="step-title">We deliver the audit.</p>
        <p>
          Within a week, you receive the full report: AI-ready processes,
          specific tools, costs, returns, and an implementation roadmap.
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>The audit is free. The upside is not.</h2>

  <p class="lede">
    We do this at no cost because the audit itself is the proof. If we can't
    find meaningful ways for AI to improve your operations, we'll tell you that
    too &mdash; and you'll have lost nothing but half an hour. If we can, you'll
    have a plan that most businesses pay consultants five figures to produce.
  </p>

  <p>
    Primorum is an AI consultancy based in Toronto. We build and integrate AI
    systems for businesses that want to grow revenue without growing headcount.
    The audit is how we earn the right to work with you.
  </p>

  <p class="cta-block">
    <a class="cta" href="mailto:audit@primorum.ai?subject=Free%20AI%20Operations%20Audit">Request your free audit &rarr;</a>
    <span class="cta-note">No cost. No commitment. No catch.</span>
  </p>
</Base>
